On the evening of March 20, two Russian SuperCam drones were destroyed in the Odessa region.

About thisreportDefense forces of South of Ukraine.

“2 Russian SuperCam UAVs were destroyed from the sea to Odessa Odessa Odessa Brigade.
Together to victory!" - The message says.

As reported by the Armyinform, on the Left Bank of the Dnieper Our WarriorsDestroyedTank, 12 guns and 140 invaders.
title: Two reconnaissance drones of Russians were knocked down in Odesa region
